- Added `ErrorBoundary` React class component wrapping the entire popup
- Shows fallback UI with error message and retry button on crash
- Refactored view switching to a `switch` statement for clarity

### `apps/extension/src/popup/components/PopupDashboard.tsx`
- **Fixed bug**: `actions` useMemo was missing `vocabCount` in dependency array — now recalculates when vocab count loads
- **Fixed bug**: `handleQuickSavePage` used two sequential `chrome.storage.local.get` calls — now parallel with `Promise.all`
- **Fixed bug**: `handleQuickSavePage` used callback-style `chrome.tabs.query` — now async/await with proper error handling
- **Fixed bug*
